Anne Morris, Project Director
Joseph Glick, Ph.D., Researcher Director

This program is supported by: Children's Bureau Office of Child Development, the National Institute of Mental Health and Mount Sinai School of Medicine of the City University of New York, the New York CIty Health Department

A gilm by Jeremy George; Vernon Riddick

Documentary footage and interviews of parents on their experiences in pediatric medical clinics.  Includes interview with Anne Morris, Project Director at the Parent Education Program, on her work at the Well Baby Clinic where parents are empowered as teachers in the development and well-being of their children.
